   },
   "source": [
    "VAE trained on 285,275 real SEC financial sequences across 6 quarters (2024q4–2026q1). Loss converged from 71.9 to 67.3 over 20 epochs. Flagged 14,264 sequences (5%) as anomalies — companies whose financial patterns deviate significantly from learned normal behavior. Model saved to Google Drive."
   ]
